<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>구직 사이트</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/jobsite.css">
</head>

<body>

    <%- include('includes/header') %>
        <%- include('includes/navbar') %>

            <div class="job-wrapper">

                <div class="job-hero">
                    <h1>구직 사이트</h1>
                    <p>원하는 사이트에서 채용공고를 바로 확인하세요</p>
                </div>

                <div class="job-grid">

                    <a href="https://www.saramin.co.kr" target="_blank" class="job-card">
                        <img src="/images/jobsite/saramin.png" class="job-logo">
                        <div class="job-info">
                            <h2>사람인</h2>
                            <p>국내 대표 채용 플랫폼</p>
                        </div>
                        <span class="job-arrow">→</span>
                    </a>

                    <a href="https://www.jobkorea.co.kr" target="_blank" class="job-card">
                        <img src="/images/jobsite/jobkorea.png" class="job-logo">
                        <div class="job-info">
                            <h2>잡코리아</h2>
                            <p>다양한 기업 채용정보</p>
                        </div>
                        <span class="job-arrow">→</span>
                    </a>

                    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/" target="_blank" class="job-card">
                        <img src="/images/jobsite/linkedin.png" class="job-logo">
                        <div class="job-info">
                            <h2>LinkedIn</h2>
                            <p>글로벌 / 해외 취업</p>
                        </div>
                        <span class="job-arrow">→</span>
                    </a>

                    <a href="https://www.wanted.co.kr" target="_blank" class="job-card">
                        <img src="/images/jobsite/wanted.png" class="job-logo">
                        <div class="job-info">
                            <h2>Wanted</h2>
                            <p>IT 중심 채용 플랫폼</p>
                        </div>
                        <span class="job-arrow">→</span>
                    </a>

                </div>
            </div>

</body>

</html>